name: Bridgetown: The Later Years (2013-2017)
description: Comics from the last five years of the Bridgetown perform, including: Allen Strickland Williams and Curtis Cook (2013), Lisa Best and Steven Wilber (2014), Dulcè Sloan and Sonia Denis (2015) and John Novosad, Ben Harkins and Shalewa Sharpe (2017).
